Find it some other day.

00:15:44.760 --> 00:15:46.239
The main thing today

00:15:46.239 --> 00:15:49.159
is to welcome our prefect came from far away.

00:15:51.799 --> 00:15:54.400
I've heard there's a capable county magistrate

00:15:54.400 --> 00:15:56.200
came to Tongling county.

00:15:57.159 --> 00:16:00.960
Today, I understand what they said is true.

00:16:00.960 --> 00:16:03.119
Thanks for your promoting.

00:16:03.799 --> 00:16:05.159
Sure.

00:16:05.719 --> 00:16:06.670
Alright.

00:16:06.670 --> 00:16:08.470
After a long trip, you must be exhausted.

00:16:08.540 --> 00:16:09.590
Why don't you go rest up.

00:16:10.159 --> 00:16:11.440
Work is more important.

