00:16:32.520 --> 00:16:34.440
all his families were also in custody.

00:16:36.479 --> 00:16:38.840
Good, hold court trial.

00:16:43.039 --> 00:16:44.119
Call...

00:16:44.119 --> 00:16:46.400
My lord, I have something to tell you.

00:16:51.159 --> 00:16:52.640
I... I'll talk to you later.

00:16:52.640 --> 00:16:54.679
Come. Stand here.

00:16:57.119 --> 00:16:58.000
Adviser Tan,

00:16:59.080 --> 00:17:01.039
meet Prefect Zong, the Prefect of Chizhou.

00:17:02.000 --> 00:17:03.080
Prefect?

