My apology.

00:17:08.800 --> 00:17:10.880
This is better seeing than hearing.

00:17:11.400 --> 00:17:14.560
A woman can be an adviser.

00:17:15.800 --> 00:17:16.839
What wrong with woman.

00:17:16.839 --> 00:17:19.118
Women can do many things as well as men.

00:17:19.118 --> 00:17:20.039
Don't be rude.

