Call the guard to bring Baba away.

00:17:23.760 --> 00:17:26.520
What a marvelous woman.

00:17:29.000 --> 00:17:31.479
I didn't teach her good manners. Please forgive her.

00:17:33.560 --> 00:17:36.959
I don't think so.

00:17:37.560 --> 00:17:38.550
Stand here.

00:17:38.740 --> 00:17:39.950
If you say something you shouldn't,

00:17:39.959 --> 00:17:41.239
I will fine you a month salary.

00:17:41.239 --> 00:17:41.760
You!

00:17:41.760 --> 00:17:42.479
One tael.

00:17:49.319 --> 00:17:51.199
Your honor, the suspect is here now.

00:18:02.640 --> 00:18:07.439
Sangjie secretly opened a gold mine, and stole the country's fortune.

00:18:08.350 --> 00:18:10.120
His relatives are suffering collateral damage.

00:18:11.250 --> 00:18:15.640
You were under the same roof top with him, day and night.

00:18:16.640 --> 00:18:18.760
Even though you've got away,

00:18:19.920 --> 00:18:22.119
