00:22:32.800 --> 00:22:34.839
How can you only thinking about love everyday.

00:22:34.839 --> 00:22:35.400
Tang!

00:22:35.400 --> 00:22:36.040
No way!

00:22:38.640 --> 00:22:40.160
Tang, only 500 taels.

00:23:01.160 --> 00:23:02.160
Does adviser Tan come back?

00:23:04.760 --> 00:23:05.359
She was,

00:23:06.599 --> 00:23:09.040
but she thought I was unfair in the trail.

00:23:09.599 --> 00:23:10.560
So she left again.

00:23:11.560 --> 00:23:13.119
Zong Yonglin seems like came for

00:23:13.119 --> 00:23:14.520
investigating Sangjie's death.

00:23:15.350 --> 00:23:17.530
But what he really wants to know

00:23:17.640 --> 00:23:18.590
is whether his servants

00:23:18.599 --> 00:23:19.959
left any information.

00:23:19.959 --> 00:23:21.680
Sangjie had dug up

00:23:21.680 --> 00:23:23.319
all the golds from a whole mountain.

00:23:23.319 --> 00:23:24.640
It can buy hundreds of Miaoshenglou,

00:23:25.359 --> 00:23:26.800
and bail the girl I love out.

00:23:27.310 --> 00:23:28.440
Plus this time,

00:23:28.680 --> 00:23:30.690
he forced me to give Sun Bufan a lighter sentence.

00:23:31.000 --> 00:23:32.800
Money can lead to god.

00:23:33.599 --> 00:23:37.719
Money can also separate a couple.

00:23:38.479 --> 00:23:40.920
How come you are talking about love all the time?

00:23:41.719 --> 00:23:43.280
Who are we now?

00:23:43.880 --> 00:23:45.839
You are a head constable earning 15 taels per month.

00:23:45.839 --> 00:23:47.800
I'm a tiny county officer earning 50 taels per month.

00:23:48.439 --> 00:23:50.359
How do we get the money to bail out the Oiran?

00:23:52.280 --> 00:23:54.199
You are right.

00:23:57.040 --> 00:23:58.760
From now on, I just have to

00:23:58.760 --> 00:24:00.880
spend more money on Miaoshenglou.

00:24:02.199 --> 00:24:05.040
I hope this Zhu Dacong have a clear mind.

00:24:05.880 --> 00:24:07.319
For the sake of adviser Tan,

00:24:07.880 --> 00:24:10.040
give me a bigger discount.

00:24:12.520 --> 00:24:13.160
Damn.

00:24:13.880 --> 00:24:14.959
Your emotion,

00:24:14.959 --> 00:24:17.439
is completely controlled by that little girl.

00:24:18.040 --> 00:24:21.199
Now she is not at the county office.

00:24:21.199 --> 00:24:23.239
And her heart is not with you either.

00:24:23.239 --> 00:24:24.760
Also go no way to her stomach.

00:24:24.760 --> 00:24:25.920
There's nothing you can do.

00:24:26.479 --> 00:24:27.430
By then,

00:24:27.430 --> 00:24:29.830
when she really becomes the wife of Miaoshenglou's proprietress,

00:24:30.800 --> 00:24:32.090
I will see what you gonna do.

00:24:33.119 --> 00:24:34.319
Boss Zhu, come, come.

00:24:37.950 --> 00:24:39.170
Why you're here?

00:24:39.400 --> 00:24:40.710
All rooms are full today,

00:24:40.710 --> 00:24:43.290
So let me stay here for a while, and I'll give you 50% off discount.

00:24:43.470 --> 00:24:43.920
Sounds good?

00:24:43.920 --> 00:24:45.050
Come on let's do it together.

00:24:58.920 --> 00:25:00.640
Magistrate Tang, Shaofeng.

00:25:01.359 --> 00:25:03.680
Today we don't talk about women.

00:25:04.359 --> 00:25:05.680
We just relax.

00:25:09.319 --> 00:25:11.800
Whatever you like, Boss.

00:25:29.040 --> 00:25:29.560
My lord.

