Did you find out his background?

00:25:42.400 --> 00:25:44.439
I checked his files from the county office,

00:25:44.439 --> 00:25:46.000
and compared with the files you gave me.

00:25:46.000 --> 00:25:47.079
There's nothing suspicious.

