no one can change the decision.

00:30:40.070 --> 00:30:42.160
If I can't even protect myself,

00:30:43.310 --> 00:30:45.040
how can I protect my citizens?

00:30:45.040 --> 00:30:47.000
So you just let the killer get away with it?

00:30:47.710 --> 00:30:49.200
Is this fair to Qi Hui?

00:30:49.400 --> 00:30:50.880
Good and evil must at last have their reward.

00:30:50.880 --> 00:30:52.350
But it hasn't to be now.

00:30:52.350 --> 00:30:54.760
Sometimes late justice is meaningless.

00:30:54.760 --> 00:30:56.920
All you are caring about is the gold case.

00:30:56.920 --> 00:30:58.590
You're totally ignored the right and wrong.

00:30:58.590 --> 00:30:59.560
If that's the case,

00:30:59.560 --> 00:31:00.870
I'd rather resign this adviser job.

00:31:01.190 --> 00:31:01.950
Then what?

00:31:02.950 --> 00:31:04.470
Go back to Jinan, and get married?

00:31:04.470 --> 00:31:05.950
What has it to do with Zhu Dacong?

00:31:07.520 --> 00:31:09.560
I said you get married, and I didn't mean Zhu Dacong.

00:31:10.160 --> 00:31:12.760
Tan Lingyin, do you really believe Zhu Dacong is the one?

00:31:12.760 --> 00:31:14.160
Who says that, what?

00:31:22.710 --> 00:31:25.310
So you really worry a lot if I'm gonna marry with Zhu Dacong?

00:31:28.470 --> 00:31:29.000
No, I'm not.

00:31:29.710 --> 00:31:30.310
Really?

00:31:31.400 --> 00:31:33.800
Not even a tiny little bit?

00:31:34.430 --> 00:31:35.070
No.

00:31:36.000 --> 00:31:36.520
No?

00:31:36.960 --> 00:31:37.650
No.

00:31:37.920 --> 00:31:38.710
Seriously no?

00:31:40.430 --> 00:31:41.190
Seriously no?

00:31:43.590 --> 00:31:44.280
Literally no?

00:31:44.280 --> 00:31:44.760
My lord.

00:31:45.680 --> 00:31:49.040
There's a Mr. Zhu in front who wanna sue adviser.

00:31:50.280 --> 00:31:50.760
Lord!

00:31:51.680 --> 00:31:53.280
You must help me out this time.

00:31:54.560 --> 00:31:55.230
Please, my lord.

00:31:56.350 --> 00:31:57.640
Please have a seat.

00:32:01.470 --> 00:32:02.640
What are you doing?

00:32:06.520 --> 00:32:07.640
My lord!

00:32:08.160 --> 00:32:09.680
I know you are very righteous,

00:32:09.680 --> 00:32:11.760
and purely black and white.

00:32:11.760 --> 00:32:13.640
But please close you eyes this time

00:32:13.640 --> 00:32:15.310
for the sake of my happiness.

00:32:16.230 --> 00:32:18.560
What are you talking about? Stand up first.

00:32:19.160 --> 00:32:19.800
My lord.

00:32:20.800 --> 00:32:23.000
Can the imperialÿenvoy appoint anyone

00:32:23.000 --> 00:32:24.800
to co-investigate the case,

00:32:24.800 --> 00:32:27.880
and report directly to your majesty?

00:32:28.400 --> 00:32:29.110
Certainly.

00:32:30.520 --> 00:32:31.710
Then do you still remember that

00:32:31.710 --> 00:32:33.400
last time you tricked landlord Sun

00:32:33.400 --> 00:32:34.880
by using the name of Tang Tianyuan?

00:32:34.880 --> 00:32:37.430
You want me to forge the imperialÿenvoy's appointment letter for you,

00:32:37.430 --> 00:32:39.400
and co-investigate the case with me?

00:32:40.040 --> 00:32:40.740
In that way,

00:32:40.950 --> 00:32:43.070
your marriage can be postponed in the name of

00:32:43.590 --> 00:32:45.550
serving the court, right?

00:32:45.620 --> 00:32:47.070
You're so clever!

00:32:47.070 --> 00:32:48.000
No way!

00:32:48.680 --> 00:32:51.560
Forgery of imperialÿenvoy's letter! It can execute me thousands of times!

00:32:51.560 --> 00:32:53.160
It's not that serious.

00:32:53.310 --> 00:32:54.400
I've already gotten a plan.

00:32:55.160 --> 00:32:57.430
Zhu Dacong is not that smart.

00:32:57.430 --> 00:32:59.400
As long as we show him the letter,

00:32:59.400 --> 00:33:01.160
we take it back and burn it at once.

00:33:01.160 --> 00:33:02.190
Besides,

00:33:02.190 --> 00:33:04.880
It's only a marriage issue of a small family.

00:33:04.880 --> 00:33:05.900
No one will care about it.

00:33:06.160 --> 00:33:09.950
If you really got exposed and died,

00:33:09.950 --> 00:33:11.760
I will give you the compensation.

00:33:11.760 --> 00:33:13.350
What can I compensate to you...

00:33:14.760 --> 00:33:15.190
I...

00:33:15.560 --> 00:33:17.050
How about I'm buried with you together?!

00:33:17.680 --> 00:33:19.520
You annoyed me when you're alive,

00:33:21.310 --> 00:33:23.430
and now you even wanna be buried with me after died?!

00:33:25.160 --> 00:33:25.830
My lord.

00:33:27.000 --> 00:33:28.830
For the happiness of the rest of my life,

00:33:28.830 --> 00:33:30.300
please help me this time.

00:33:30.520 --> 00:33:32.190
I don't want to bother others either.

00:33:32.190 --> 00:33:34.110
But I'm really out of clues.

00:33:35.590 --> 00:33:36.720
This will be the last time.

00:33:41.110 --> 00:33:42.290
So it means you're gonna help me?

00:33:45.830 --> 00:33:46.470
Make the ink ready.

00:33:52.130 --> 00:33:53.880
My lord you are really the best lord

00:33:53.880 --> 00:33:55.070
of the world.

00:33:59.560 --> 00:34:00.800
Don't think too much.

00:34:01.430 --> 00:34:03.470
It's only because the drum in front of our gate

00:34:03.470 --> 00:34:05.040
is going to be beaten by him.

00:34:05.040 --> 00:34:06.040
It makes my head exploded.

00:34:26.080 --> 00:34:27.429
You are getting addicted by using

00:34:27.429 --> 00:34:28.519
the name of Tang Tianyuan.

00:34:29.040 --> 00:34:30.230
Even the stamp looks so real.

00:34:30.230 --> 00:34:30.840
Don't touch.

00:34:31.389 --> 00:34:32.599
It's fake anyway.

00:34:34.600 --> 00:34:36.190
Whether it's fake or not,

00:34:36.190 --> 00:34:37.150
it saved your life.

00:34:41.230 --> 00:34:41.670
Tell me,

00:34:42.320 --> 00:34:43.180
How will you thank me?

00:34:44.760 --> 00:34:46.390
Let me think...

00:34:46.949 --> 00:34:47.599
I...

00:34:48.630 --> 00:34:49.760
I will tell you when I know it.

00:34:55.630 --> 00:34:56.760
Stop knocking on that!

00:34:56.760 --> 00:34:57.560
Who are you?

00:34:57.560 --> 00:34:58.120
Come over here.

00:34:58.120 --> 00:34:58.760
This is big.

00:35:00.080 --> 00:35:00.630
Get off me.

00:35:02.710 --> 00:35:04.320
Magistrate Tang, I am going to sue...

00:35:05.230 --> 00:35:06.670
sue this heartless woman.

00:35:07.190 --> 00:35:08.230
What are you talking about?

00:35:08.760 --> 00:35:09.800
What's your accusation?

00:35:09.800 --> 00:35:11.600
Run away from wedding and break an engagement.

00:35:12.280 --> 00:35:13.910
We've been engaged long time ago,

00:35:13.910 --> 00:35:15.280
but she has been postponing it.

00:35:15.840 --> 00:35:17.940
She disobeyed parental commands and matchmaker's words.

00:35:18.470 --> 00:35:20.300
And she's also dissolute working in the county.

00:35:20.470 --> 00:35:22.080
I came from far away to look for her.

00:35:22.760 --> 00:35:25.150
Please help me get my justice done, your honor.

00:35:27.040 --> 00:35:29.950
Please have a look. This is the marriage contract.

00:35:30.840 --> 00:35:32.150
It was made by my father's second wife.

00:35:32.150 --> 00:35:33.320
I didn't know of this contract.

00:35:33.840 --> 00:35:36.000
Okay. I will give your justice back to you.

00:35:36.560 --> 00:35:37.280
Guards.

00:35:37.280 --> 00:35:38.040
Here.

00:35:40.190 --> 00:35:42.470
Paddle him 15 strikes, and 20 taels for penalty fee.

00:35:42.840 --> 00:35:43.250
Yes!

00:35:43.430 --> 00:35:44.000
Wait!

00:35:44.800 --> 00:35:46.120
You want to beat me again?

00:35:47.360 --> 00:35:48.760
Everyone, have a look!

00:35:48.760 --> 00:35:51.140
This is our county magistrate

00:35:51.320 --> 00:35:52.600
who's not ruling his case by law.

00:35:52.600 --> 00:35:55.390
Bro, the way you are acting now.

00:35:55.390 --> 00:35:57.470
Girls will not in love you.

00:35:58.630 --> 00:35:59.390
What do you know.

00:36:00.230 --> 00:36:00.870
Magistrate Tang.

00:36:01.870 --> 00:36:03.120
Even if you wanna beat me today,

00:36:03.710 --> 00:36:04.840
at least you should tell me

00:36:05.390 --> 00:36:06.910
which law did I break.

00:36:08.600 --> 00:36:10.430
Adviser, show him.

00:36:12.430 --> 00:36:14.040
You do have the marriage contract,

00:36:14.040 --> 00:36:15.190
but I forget to tell you that

00:36:15.190 --> 00:36:16.840
I'm appointed by the imperialÿenvoy directly

00:36:16.840 --> 00:36:18.040
as the adviser of Tongling.

00:36:19.120 --> 00:36:20.100
Do you know what this is?

00:36:20.630 --> 00:36:22.430
This is the appointment letter written by himself.

00:36:22.430 --> 00:36:24.600
Making me to co-investigate the gold case,

00:36:25.600 --> 00:36:27.470
stamped by the purple gold-stone stamp.

00:36:27.470 --> 00:36:29.200
I'm the adviser appointed by the court.

00:36:29.250 --> 00:36:31.120
Having an important duty. So how can I committed to a marriage?

00:36:31.120 --> 00:36:32.150
Do you wanna against the court?

00:36:33.840 --> 00:36:34.710
How can it be?

00:36:35.560 --> 00:36:37.280
Show me the letter.

00:36:37.800 --> 00:36:38.630
Why not.

00:36:40.320 --> 00:36:42.120
Adviser Tan's capability,

00:36:42.120 --> 00:36:44.670
is witnessed by the whole citizen of Tongling County.

00:36:44.670 --> 00:36:46.360
Our county office can't operate without her.

00:36:47.120 --> 00:36:49.430
Zhu Dacong, you are in contempt of court.

00:36:49.430 --> 00:36:50.930
This is already a fair light penalty for you.

00:36:51.060 --> 00:36:51.760
Fine.

00:36:52.870 --> 00:36:54.280
Being an adviser, right?

00:36:54.280 --> 00:36:55.710
There must be a term of it.

00:36:56.560 --> 00:36:59.080
My father said that for a temporary appointed task,

00:36:59.080 --> 00:37:01.230
the term is only for 3 months.

00:37:01.760 --> 00:37:03.870
3 months won't be a problem.

00:37:03.870 --> 00:37:05.670
I don't believe it.

00:37:05.670 --> 00:37:07.000
Will the court be in charge of

00:37:07.000 --> 00:37:08.870
the happy marriage of county's adviser.

00:37:09.630 --> 00:37:12.710
Tan Lingyin, you are mine.

00:37:17.470 --> 00:37:18.280
What shall we do now?

00:37:28.360 --> 00:37:30.870
My lord, how could you only wrote 3 months?!

00:37:30.870 --> 00:37:32.910
You should write it as forever.

00:37:33.080 --> 00:37:35.040
Forever? Why don't you just kill me directly?!

00:37:35.760 --> 00:37:37.800
We are on the same boat now,

00:37:37.800 --> 00:37:39.600
and I don't have any choice, do I?

00:37:40.360 --> 00:37:41.630
In my view,

00:37:41.630 --> 00:37:43.840
you are quite willing to do it.

00:37:43.840 --> 00:37:46.040
Did you prepare the silk for me?

00:37:46.040 --> 00:37:46.560
How can you

00:37:46.560 --> 00:37:47.910
be so unappreciative!

00:37:48.600 --> 00:37:49.840
How can it be.

00:37:50.560 --> 00:37:50.910
My lord.

00:37:51.470 --> 00:37:53.360
Shall I be your adviser,

00:37:53.360 --> 00:37:54.230
forever?

00:37:57.390 --> 00:37:57.910
Right side.

00:38:00.560 --> 00:38:00.910
My lord!

00:38:04.120 --> 00:38:05.630
My lord, prefect Zong wanna see you.

00:38:06.360 --> 00:38:07.190
Why don't you come with me.

00:38:07.870 --> 00:38:08.560
Shall I come too?

00:38:12.520 --> 00:38:13.280
You stay here.

00:38:16.230 --> 00:38:18.190
Lingyin bid farewell to your honor.

00:38:30.950 --> 00:38:31.870
I'm free!

00:38:33.870 --> 00:38:35.840
I don't need to get marry with Zhu Dacong anymore!

00:38:41.430 --> 00:38:42.070
Prefect Zong.

00:38:42.320 --> 00:38:44.600
What kind of thing which is not appropriate to discuss in the office?

00:38:46.870 --> 00:38:48.950
I heard that in our Tongling County,

00:38:49.470 --> 00:38:52.840
Miaoshenglou's dishes are the best.

00:38:53.470 --> 00:38:58.280
I'm a foodie.

00:38:58.280 --> 00:39:01.600
So I'd love to try it out. Is magistrate Tang

00:39:02.230 --> 00:39:03.600
don't wanna have a meal with me?

00:39:03.600 --> 00:39:04.660
What are you talking about?

00:39:05.630 --> 00:39:06.230
After you.

00:39:07.230 --> 00:39:07.760
Please,

00:39:07.760 --> 00:39:08.040
Come.

00:39:09.870 --> 00:39:11.470
When we just arrived at here,

00:39:12.870 --> 00:39:15.120
we heard something interest.

00:39:16.360 --> 00:39:19.150
It was about the lady adviser of your office.

00:39:20.520 --> 00:39:22.520
What is her name? Tan...

00:39:22.520 --> 00:39:23.190
Tan Lingyin.

00:39:24.670 --> 00:39:26.530
She is quite good at communication

00:39:26.590 --> 00:39:28.000
which can give a speech just like that.

00:39:28.000 --> 00:39:30.600
I didn't manage my staffs well. Please forgive me.

00:39:32.560 --> 00:39:35.430
Generally speaking, the county office should have one adviser for

00:39:35.430 --> 00:39:39.120
each one of the criminal investigate, accounting, communist party,

00:39:39.120 --> 00:39:42.390
management tasks.

00:39:43.950 --> 00:39:46.040
Which of these parts is she doing?

00:39:46.710 --> 00:39:49.280
She... she is doing bit of all of the them.

00:39:50.190 --> 00:39:54.040
I see, then she must be tired.

00:39:56.710 --> 00:39:59.630
But magistrate Tang, you can't treat your employee like this.

00:40:01.710 --> 00:40:02.230
Well,

00:40:03.080 --> 00:40:04.760
there's a person came with me this time.

00:40:04.760 --> 00:40:05.600
Chen Shaoxing.

00:40:07.670 --> 00:40:08.950
He comes from the east river region.

00:40:09.710 --> 00:40:12.870
Although he didn't make it through the national exam,

00:40:14.000 --> 00:40:15.870
but he can do his work very well.

00:40:17.710 --> 00:40:21.030
I shall leave him in Tongling with you

00:40:22.000 --> 00:40:23.230
to help you with your heavy tasks.

00:40:23.760 --> 00:40:26.520
In terms of the lady adviser,

00:40:27.950 --> 00:40:29.120
a woman,

00:40:30.840 --> 00:40:32.350
showing her face around all the time.

00:40:34.000 --> 00:40:35.320
It will hurt her reputation.

00:40:36.520 --> 00:40:37.600
Why don't you

00:40:37.600 --> 00:40:39.230
dismiss her now?
